    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 is a mechanical masterpiece, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut and responsive, benefiting from factory-spec suspension geometry and zero subframe fatigue. Finished in a flawless Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this example boasts impeccable compression numbers and a comprehensive service history. It offers a visceral, analog driving experience with a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline that remains as sharp as the day it left Regensburg.",
